About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. “Alpha”, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

GROUP STAGE DAY 1 | JULY 25

2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP ka aghaaz ho chuka hai ESPORTS WORLD CUP ke sath, aik dhamakedar Group Stage k pehle din ke sath! Tayyar ho jao ek aur shaandaar summer ke liye jab duniya ki top PUBG MOBILE teams Riyadh mein takraayengi glory ,legacy , aur $3,000,000 ke inaam ke liye. Aao mil kar dekhein ke kaunsi teams HEAT ko BEAT kar paengi!

Yeh global showdown duniya bhar ki behtareen squads ko ikattha karta hai, jo sab 2025 PMWC jo k EWC ki taraf sy horha hai jeetne ka khwab le kar tayyar hain. Pehle ka aaghaz dhamakedaar matches ke saath hoga, jo agle teen dinon ki sakht muqabla baazi ka manzar zahir kryga.

Is safar ka aaghaz Group Stage se hoga, jahan 24 teams ko 3 groups mein taqseem kiya gya hai jo Grand Finals ke liye apni jagah banane ke liye takrayen gi. Is stage se top 8 teams seedha Grand Finals mein pohnchyn gi, jabke baaqi 16 teams high pressure Survival Stage mein aamna saamna karen gi aakhri 8 slots ke liye. Grand Finals mein 16 behtareen teams ek doosre ke khilaaf glory, pride, aur championship ka taaj pehnny k liye pury josh se takraengi.

🔥 Ap 2025 PMWC jo k EWC mai horha hai miss nahe krna chahyngy.

- Dekho duniya ki top PUBG MOBILE teams ko Riyadh mein apne waqar ke liye takraate hue!
- Har match mein high-stakes action ka lutf uthao, jo har dafa is dorh ko badal kar rakh dega.
- Apne pasandeeda region aur teamon ko cheer karo jab woh $3,000,000 aur  ke taj k peche bhaag rahe hongy!
- Grand Finals mein hoga zabardast SMASH RULE format to tayyar ho jao excitement ke liye!

🔥 SMASH RULE Grand Finals mein kaise kaam karta hai?

Grand Finals ke doosry din ke baad, Match Point Threshold set kiya jata hai jo ke #1 ranked team ke points mai 10 points jamah kr k banta hai. Jo bhi team is threshold ko cross karti hai, usay phir kisi baad wale match mein jeet hasil karni hoti hai taake woh trophy apne naam kar sake, jis match mein woh threshold cross karti hai, agar usi mein jeeti to bhi woh champion nahi banegi.

Agar Match 18 tak koi team SMASH Rule ke zariye title secure nahi karti, to standard rules ke mutabiq sabse zyada total points wali team ko winner declare kiya jata hai.

LYRICS:
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga
Ali viraasat hai Mustafa ki, Ali hi mash’hood-e-haq rahe ga

Tu wo walad hai jo lam-yalid ke makaan se jalwa-numa hua hai
Tu nashir-e-dawa-e-salooni, tu kya hai? Sab ko guman hua hai
Tu qasim-e-noor-e-Mustafa hai, tu nafs-e-Payghambar-e-Khuda hai
Tu markaz-e-Awliya-e-alam, tu bil-yaqeen fakhr-e-Ambiya hai

Ali mizaaj-e-Muhammadi hai, Ali to asrar-e-haq rahe ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Tu hi Risaalat ki hai khilafat, tu hi wilayat tu hi imamat
Tu kurra-e-arz-e-Kibriya pe Nabi ki hai awaleen shahadat
Tu mehvar-e-ilm-e-do-sara hai, tu kashif-e-maqsad-e-ibadat
Tu hai siraat-e-nijaat-e-insaan, hai qalb-e-momin teri riyasat

Tumhara rahbar tumhain mubarak, hamara rahbar Ali rahe ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Wo badr ho ya mubahila ho, ya phir Muhammad ki wo kisaa ho
Wo chahe Marhab ka samna ho, ya phir wo khandaq ka ma’rka ho
Uhud mein dhaal-e-Payambari ya, buton ka Ka’be se khaatma ho
Ya wo wilayat ki taaj-poshi ba-dast-e-at'haar-e-Mustafa ho

Ali se daman bachane wale, Ali tujhe jaa ba jaa mile ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Nabi ke deen ki ragon mein Haider lahu ki soorat ravaan rahe ga
Ali ka munkir zaleel-o-ruswa azal se tha hashr tak rahe ga
Ali hi haq tha Ali hi haq hai Ali ki naslon mein haq rahe ga

Bus Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali ...

Aao ji Ali Ali wird paka laiyay
Ghaman nu chadd aj khushiyan mana laiyay
Ral ke aakhiye, “Baad Muhammad
Sab ton afzal zikr-e-Ali" Bus

Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali Bus ...

Ali de chehre nu takna ibadat
Ali da naan loko japna ibadat
Ki ki mein dassan tenu sifat Ali di
Jane Ali nu Khuda Ya Nabi bus

Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali Bus ...

Haider, safdar, sher-e-ghazanfar
Rahbar-e-akbar, mard-e-muzaffar
At'har, azhar, Haq da mazhar
Peeng de andar cheereya azdar
Deen da anbar, Khvaja Qambar
Veer Paighambar, awwal number
Baad Muhammad sab ton bartar
Ikko baan nal puteya Khyber
Ilm samandar, fakhr-e-Sikandar
Mard-e-Qalandar, loon loon andar
Badr ton lay ke Khandak, Khyber
Dushman cheer ke langeya Haider
Tayyab, tahir, banda-parwar
Rooh-e-munawwar, maula, sarwar
Hadi, mahdi, aali-gauhar
Zahra paak da suchha shauhar
Qazi-e-azam, alim-e-alam
Shams-e-wilayat, Noor-e-hidayat
Aashiq Rab da, Paak nasab da
Ghaiz ghazab da, Hunar kasab da
Mahir sab da, Fakhr Arab da
Baap Hassan da, Phol chaman da
Raah adan da, shah zaman da 
Waar Ali da, kair Khuda da
Ishq Ali da, lutf Khuda da
Bol Ali de, hukam Khuda da
Deed Ali di, karam Khuda da

Bus Ali Ali Bus Ali Ali Bus ...
